| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4872 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c5a75614-2fd4-5cfe-8246-92d5ee4bae6a"
